 pictures<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tEven Hodge himself was impressed by how creative he was becoming. As he was driving towards the restaurant, these were the things he was thinking about. Yeah, perhaps he should even try for himself the pizza from that restaurant, to find out why the place was so popular. It was quite surprising given the pizza shop was so close to his Club 1997 and yet he had never tried the food there before. Hodge was not sure if food was served twenty-four seven there, but it would not be hard for him to drop by there when he had time.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167882011573/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p788007/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p788007\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796603/\">小贝大儿子17岁的人生是这样的 看完我很受伤</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796625/\">2016年iphone摄影赛获奖作品：一半来自中国</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795486/\">82%英国人都会读错的10个单词：挑战试试？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p795700/\">每天都很累吗？做好3件小事让生活焕然一新</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796128/\">教学10年的老外告诉你：美国人最常的俚语</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796585/\">真正说走就走的冒险：目的地未知，你来吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p796601/\">新外长鲍里斯 终于把英国政界变成了部喜剧片</a></li><li style=\"m